responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "A8CD15954F7E0771B21FEEBC6048AF0F", "You would do well to strike these cursed blackbirds from the skies, lest they carry the stink of their goblin masters to your own settlements. I will tolerate your presence in my range whilst you do, and if I am pleased with your efforts, I will bless your passage as you leave our range.")
